and clinics, I moved to the United States, where my passion for design evolved into a new chapter.<\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p>Together with my wife, we established <strong>Saloni Furniture Virginia<\/strong>, where I manage interior design consultations, project management, and store operations, helping our clients create beautiful and functional living spaces.<\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p>In my free time, I love staying active, discovering new places, and spending quality time with my loved ones. I care deeply about animals and nature, and we share our home with our two cats.<\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p>I believe that design has the power to transform lives, and I look forward to meeting you and bringing your dream space to life.<\/p>","expiration_date":"","button_label":"","button_link":"shopify:\/\/collections","button_style":"button--style-2","button_style_hover_outline":false}},"image_with_text_gNgMQT":{"type":"image-with-text","custom_css":[".section__inner {max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;}","h2 {text-transform: capitalize;}"],"settings":{"overwrite_colors":false,"color":"#000000","background":"#ffffff","overlay_color":"linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 100%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 1) 100%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 1) 100%)","enable_wide":true,"gap":false,"flip":false,"layout":"50-50","image_width":30,"aspect_ratio_desktop":"media--1-1","aspect_ratio_mobile":"media--mobile-1-1","image_position":"top","image_desktop":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/test-image.webp","content_horizontal_align":"left","content_size":"small","content_large_gap":true,"pre_heading":"","heading":"Sirin Ozdemir – Co-Founder & Designer","subheading":"<p>Hi, I’m Sirin. I have been working as a designer since 2017, blending creativity and functionality to craft inspiring living spaces. My design journey began in Europe, where I managed and designed for a Saloni store, helping clients transform their homes with carefully curated pieces and personalized design support.<\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p>In 2023, I embarked on a new chapter by establishing <strong>Saloni Furniture Virginia<\/strong> in the United States, where I continue to pursue my passion for creating spaces that reflect each client’s lifestyle while ensuring comfort and elegance.<\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p>Outside of design, I enjoy exploring different forms of handcrafts and am passionate about supporting local animal shelters whenever I can. I believe that a well-designed space can enhance everyday life, and I look forward to helping you create a home that feels uniquely yours.<\/p>","expiration_date":"","button_label":"","button_link":"shopify:\/\/collections","button_style":"button--style-2","button_style_hover_outline":false}},"custom_liquid_F8Nk9W":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"t:sections.custom-liquid.name","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<div class=\"sf-steps-section-bg\">\n  <div class=\"sf-steps-section\">\n\n    <!-- Call Us Section -->\n    <a class=\"sf-step\" href=\"tel:+12029759995\">\n      <div class=\"contact-container\">\n        <div class=\"icon-container\">\n          <svg fill=\"#000000\" width=\"40px\" height=\"40px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n            <path d=\"M6.62,10.79C8.06,13.62 10.38,15.94 13.21,17.38L15.41,15.18C15.69,14.9 16.08,14.82 16.43,14.93C17.55,15.3 18.75,15.5 20,15.5A1,1 0 0,1 21,16.5V20A1,1 0 0,1 20,21A17,17 0 0,1 3,4A1,1 0 0,1 4,3H7.5A1,1 0 0,1 8.5,4C8.5,5.25 8.7,6.45 9.07,7.57C9.18,7.92 9.1,8.31 8.82,8.59L6.62,10.79Z\"\/>\n          <\/svg>\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"contact-info\">\n          <h3 class=\"title-custom\">Get In Touch<\/h3>\n          <p>+1 (202) 975 9995<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/a>\n\n    <!-- Text Us Section -->\n    <a class=\"sf-step\" href=\"mailto:info@salonifurnitureus.com\">\n      <div class=\"contact-container\">\n        <div class=\"icon-container\">\n          <svg fill=\"#000000\" width=\"40px\" height=\"40px\" viewBox=\"0 0 25.6 25.6\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n            <titl